EU Says More European Banks May Need Recapitalization in Future

-- B y   J i m   B r u n s d e n
-- 
2011-09-23T10:32:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-23/eu-says-more-european-banks-may-need-recapitalization-in-future.html
More banks may need
recapitalizations in the European Union, said Olivier Bailly, a
spokesman for the European Commission.  “It is possible that some other banks may need to be
recapitalized in the future,” he said. “We have the
mechanisms, will be ready.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
